{
  "displayName": "Discord Bot - Observability Dashboard V2",
  "etag": "8316db0b238f13c7769ada96bbfa7c7c",
  "mosaicLayout": {
    "columns": 48,
    "tiles": [
      {
        "height": 16,
        "width": 24,
        "widget": {
          "title": "📈 Requêtes par service (req/min)",
          "xyChart": {
            "chartOptions": {
              "mode": "COLOR"
            },
            "dataSets": [
              {
                "plotType": "LINE",
                "targetAxis": "Y1",
                "timeSeriesQuery": {
                  "timeSeriesFilter": {
                    "aggregation": {
                      "alignmentPeriod": "60s",
                      "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_SUM",
                      "groupByFields": [
                        "resource.labels.service_name"
                      ],
                      "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_RATE"
                    },
                    "filter": "resource.type=\"cloud_run_revision\" AND metric.type=\"run.googleapis.com/request_count\""
                  }
                }
              }
            ],
            "yAxis": {
              "label": "Requêtes/min",
              "scale": "LINEAR"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "height": 16,
        "width": 24,
        "xPos": 24,
        "widget": {
          "title": "⏱️ Latence P95 par service (ms)",
          "xyChart": {
            "chartOptions": {
              "mode": "COLOR"
            },
            "dataSets": [
              {
                "plotType": "LINE",
                "targetAxis": "Y1",
                "timeSeriesQuery": {
                  "timeSeriesFilter": {
                    "aggregation": {
                      "alignmentPeriod": "60s",
                      "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_PERCENTILE_95",
                      "groupByFields": [
                        "resource.labels.service_name"
                      ],
                      "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_DELTA"
                    },
                    "filter": "resource.type=\"cloud_run_revision\" AND metric.type=\"run.googleapis.com/request_latencies\""
                  }
                }
              }
            ],
            "yAxis": {
              "label": "Latence P95 (ms)",
              "scale": "LINEAR"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "height": 16,
        "width": 24,
        "yPos": 16,
        "widget": {
          "title": "🔴 Taux d'erreur par service (%)",
          "xyChart": {
            "chartOptions": {
              "mode": "COLOR"
            },
            "dataSets": [
              {
                "plotType": "LINE",
                "targetAxis": "Y1",
                "timeSeriesQuery": {
                  "timeSeriesFilterRatio": {
                    "denominator": {
                      "aggregation": {
                        "alignmentPeriod": "60s",
                        "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_SUM",
                        "groupByFields": [
                          "resource.labels.service_name"
                        ],
                        "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_RATE"
                      },
                      "filter": "resource.type=\"cloud_run_revision\" AND metric.type=\"run.googleapis.com/request_count\""
                    },
                    "numerator": {
                      "aggregation": {
                        "alignmentPeriod": "60s",
                        "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_SUM",
                        "groupByFields": [
                          "resource.labels.service_name"
                        ],
                        "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_RATE"
                      },
                      "filter": "resource.type=\"cloud_run_revision\" AND metric.type=\"run.googleapis.com/request_count\" AND metric.labels.response_code_class=\"5xx\""
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            ],
            "yAxis": {
              "label": "Taux d'erreur",
              "scale": "LINEAR"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "height": 26,
        "width": 24,
        "xPos": 24,
        "yPos": 16,
        "widget": {
          "title": "📝 Logs ERROR récents",
          "logsPanel": {
            "filter": "jsonPayload.severity=\"ERROR\"\nOR severity=\"ERROR\"",
            "resourceNames": [
              "projects/serverless-ejguidon-dev/locations/global/logScopes/_Default"
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "height": 16,
        "width": 48,
        "yPos": 42,
        "widget": {
          "title": "🔍 Accès rapide - Cloud Trace & Logs",
          "text": {
            "content": "## 🔗 Liens rapides vers les outils d'observabilité\n\n### Cloud Trace\n- [📊 Toutes les traces](https://console.cloud.google.com/traces/list?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev)\n- [🐌 Traces lentes (>1s)](https://console.cloud.google.com/traces/list?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev&minLatency=1000ms)\n- [❌ Traces avec erreurs](https://console.cloud.google.com/traces/list?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev&f=traceFilter:HAS%3A%22error%22)\n\n### Logs Explorer\n- [📋 Tous les logs structurés](https://console.cloud.google.com/logs/query?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev&query=resource.type%3D%22cloud_run_revision%22)\n- [🔴 Logs ERROR uniquement](https://console.cloud.google.com/logs/query?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev&query=resource.type%3D%22cloud_run_revision%22%20AND%20severity%3D%22ERROR%22)\n\n### Services Cloud Run\n- [proxy](https://console.cloud.google.com/run/detail/europe-west1/proxy/metrics?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev)\n- [processor-base](https://console.cloud.google.com/run/detail/europe-west1/processor-base/metrics?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev)\n- [processor-art](https://console.cloud.google.com/run/detail/europe-west1/processor-art/metrics?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev)\n- [user-manager](https://console.cloud.google.com/run/detail/europe-west1/user-manager/metrics?project=serverless-ejguidon-dev)\n\n---\n\n**💡 Tip**: Utilisez `correlation_id` pour suivre une requête à travers tous les services",
            "format": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "height": 12,
        "width": 12,
        "yPos": 58,
        "widget": {
          "title": "💻 CPU Utilization - Tous services",
